    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase funding for the DVLA to reduce delays to medical license decisions ",
        "additional_details": "We urge the Government to increase funding for the DVLA to shorten the time to process these decisions within an 8-week window and provide mobility allowances for those affected by delays.",
        "background": "We believe the current process for DVLA decisions on medical driving licenses can cause significant delays and hardship for individuals unable to drive until a decision is made",
